author: kwall
msg: QPID-4112: Virtualhosts recover exchanges before queues
Switch the recover order from queues,exchanges,... to exchanges,queues,.. so that when a queue with an alternate exchange
is recovered, the exchange's uuid is already in the registry.

author: stsp
msg: (edit_chunk): If no editor could be found, print the correct error message
even if error tracing is enabled. This used to print "traced call" and now
prints the expected message for SVN_ERR_CL_NO_EXTERNAL_EDITOR.
